title: A New Therapy for Health & Energy - Richard Clark - Mantesh
description:
Books : Medicine and Health : English
In Epub & Mobi
Updated June 2015. A simple, easy to use therapy for self use at home. Nothing is taken. It's effective and safe having been developed over 20 years and it works on many conditions. The materials used are inexpensive, household items easily obtained. This book contains a free step-by-step guide showing how to use The Therapy. Many have tried it over the years and it's hoped you will as well
